  "description": "This 2017 Skoda Fabia TSI SE presents an exceptional opportunity with its remarkably low mileage of just 31,000 miles. This well maintained example, finished in the SE trim, is powered by an efficient 1.2 litre petrol engine and meets Euro 6 emissions standards. Inside, you'll find comfort and convenience with manual air conditioning and the impressive Arkamys Surround Sound Package, complete with a branded sound system. Connectivity is made simple with integrated Bluetooth, and parking is made easier thanks to the rear parking sensors.\n\nThe Skoda Fabia TSI SE stands out from the crowd with several key advantages. Its fuel economy is a significant highlight, achieving an impressive 60 miles per gallon, which will help keep running costs down. Furthermore, this model falls into a low insurance group, making it an economical choice for many drivers. You'll also appreciate the generous boot space, offering practicality for shopping trips or holidays. With low CO2 emissions, it's also a more environmentally conscious option. For those who enjoy a responsive drive, the 0 to 60 miles per hour acceleration is achieved in a brisk 9.1 seconds.",
